{"type":null,"faqId":45465,"title":"华为盒子在电视画面显示不满屏、比例失调或超出屏幕显示区域怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>可能是显示区域的设置有问题，请进入盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 显示区域</span><span>”，按遥控器方向键 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165080\" style=\"width:0.38055557in;height:0.35416666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，调整画面的显示区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165081\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span>可能是华为盒子的屏幕比例与电视机不一致。请进入盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; 屏幕比例</span><span>”，传统电视请设置为 4:3，高清电视请设置为 16:9。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165082\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span>电视机本身的显示区域有问题，请根据实际显示效果。调整电视机的显示区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>部分视频本身为固定的长宽比，此时屏幕显示黑边，属于正常现象。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":247,"faqType":"显示","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"985","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557785000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":15,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不满屏,比例失调,超出屏幕","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}